## ğŸ¨ Log Format

Every log includes:

* âœ… Username (resolved automatically or via server)
* ğŸ“ Module directory
* â±ï¸ Timestamp
* ğŸ“¦ Level (INFO, ERROR, etc.)
* ğŸ“ Message

Sample (terminal):

```
(username @ myapp) ğŸ¤Œ CL Timing: [ 2025-08-04T11:23:52 ]
[ INFO ] Server started on port 8000
ğŸ
```

